data.description: **RATE BUYDOWN AVAILABLE WITH APPROVED OFFER** Experience resort-style living at its finest in this exquisite four-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom sanctuary spanning 2,420 square feet of pure luxury. Nestled within the highly acclaimed Bellalago, a distinguished Resort-Style Residential Community, this home offers unparalleled access to a world of amenities and comfort.    Situated just a short 30-minute drive from the enchantment of Walt Disney World and numerous major attractions, Bellalago is a prestigious 24-hour guarded and gated private community. Within these gates lies a plethora of exclusive amenities designed to elevate your lifestyle.    Indulge in the community's own Bellalago Academy, delight in dining at Flip Flops Restaurant with its full poolside bar, and revel in the refreshing waters of the JR Olympic-size pool complete with a water park and a kiddie pool. A spa awaits your relaxation, along with a team of dedicated staff and managers ensuring every moment is exceptional.    Fitness enthusiasts will find their haven with multiple fitness centers, an aerobics room, and expert yoga and fitness trainers on hand. Nature lovers can explore fishing piers, boat docks, walking and biking trails, and relish in outdoor activities like basketball, tennis, volleyball, and barbecue gatherings in dedicated areas – the epitome of a vibrant community lifestyle.    Step inside this immaculate home where comfort meets sophistication. The spacious layout boasts a large flex room adaptable for a 5th bedroom or a tranquil nursery. The kitchen, a chef's dream, features top-of-the-line quartz counters, tall wood cabinets, and stainless steel appliances - perfect for culinary endeavors or casual family meals.    This isn't just a home; it's a lifestyle. Experience the feeling of a perpetual vacation within the comforts of your own space. Come and see for yourself the sheer opulence and endless possibilities this Bellalago gem offers.
